titles.title: To extend the suspension of duty on 2,2 -(2,5-Thiophenediyl)bis(5-(1,1-dimethylethyl) benzoxazole).

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary:
12/11/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the suspension of duty on 2,2 -(2,5-Thiophenediyl)bis(5-(1,1-dimethylethyl) benzoxazole).
